This paper deals with the use of text generation techniques to augment the training data of artificial agents, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of generative models for image data, which could also place it under computer vision (cs.CV).
